    <link href="http://singaloud.tk/2014/05/06/%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3-linux-%E4%B8%8B-sublime-text-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5/"/>
    <id>http://singaloud.tk/2014/05/06/完美解决-linux-下-sublime-text-中文输入/</id>
    <published>2014-05-06T11:36:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-05-06T15:19:47.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a id="more"></a><br><em><em>声明：此文非原创，而是综合了若干人的工作而成</em><br><em>参考文章见文末</em></em></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="测试环境：">测试环境：</h2>
<p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
3
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="tag">OS</span><span class="pseudo">:linuxmint16_x64(xfce)</span>
<span class="tag">Fcitx</span><span class="pseudo">:4</span><span class="class">.2</span><span class="class">.8</span><span class="class">.3</span>
<span class="tag">sublime_text</span><span class="pseudo">:3059</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="第一步">第一步</h3>
<ul>
<li>将下列代码保存为<code>subsublime-imfix.c</code><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8
